item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Immortals of Aveum (Original soundtrack)
item.description:
Hello guys,
i would really appreciate if someone would take their time and upload the soundtrack album of this game (Immortals of Aveum). It's available on both Itunes and Amazon Music but unfortunately neither offer purchasing options for the country i'm in (Romania).

Much obliged,
Mike
